{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>BUILD and MANAGE</strong></h2>Construct a massive space station using blocks, featuring capsule hotels, karaoke bars, cozy sofas, and attractive decor. Oversee the production chains for electricity, goods, and spare parts, utilizing small drones. Turn these operations into a profitable venture!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571990/extras/2022-08-22-construction.gif?t=1724672894\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>MAKE CONTACT with ALIENS</strong></h2>Interact with 15 unique alien races, each with distinct characteristics\u2014ranging from humanoid to cybernetic and paradoxical life forms. Their appearances and behaviors vary widely, with virtually infinite variations in faces and bodies thanks to procedural generation.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1571990/extras/2022-08-22-arrival.gif?t=1724672894\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FIND THE MONSTERS AND CRIMINALS</strong></h2>Your station is a hotbed for criminals\u2014pyromaniacs, thieves, mimics, and cyber-hackers. Carefully check documents, be on the lookout for anomalies, and keep an eye on suspicious activity. Automate surveillance and verification processes to maintain security.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>PLAY ENDLESS STORY!</strong></h2>Choose from two game modes: a story-driven mode with multiple endings or an endless gameplay mode. Procedurally generated events keep the gameplay fresh and engaging. Facing a beetle parasite outbreak? Messes near the elevator? Mysterious traders? Economic inflation? Expect the Extraterrestrial Galactic Government to step in soon!<br><br>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Researcher","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1571990/605e5c649bc258cf13543efa95af2eacd014e003.jpg"},{"name":"The Naturalist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com